---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing" description="Simple, transparent pricing for Barrel databases. Self-host free, or get support and Barrel Console.">
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-barrel-gray/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Both databases are 100% open source. Self-host free, or get support and Barrel Console.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Support Tiers Section -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-coral/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Support Plans</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-center mb-8">Per-instance pricing. Mix and match based on your needs.</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
          <!-- Community -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Community</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">Free</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Forever</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Full open source
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                GitLab issues
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Community support
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://gitlab.enki.io/barrel-db" class="block w-full text-center bg-teal-dark/20 hover:bg-teal-dark/30 text-barrel-gray py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm">
              View Source
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Basic -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-coral/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Basic</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">29<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mo</span></p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Per instance</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Email support
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                72h response time
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Business hours
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu/subscribe/basic" class="block w-full text-center bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-semibold">
              Subscribe
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Standard -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-coral/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Standard</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">99<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mo</span></p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Per instance</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                8x5 support
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                24h response time
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Deployment help
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu/subscribe/standard" class="block w-full text-center bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-semibold">
              Subscribe
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Professional -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-coral p-6 relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-coral text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">
              Popular
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Professional</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">249<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mo</span></p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Per instance</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                24x5 support
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                4h critical response
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-coral mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Priority tickets
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu/subscribe/professional" class="block w-full text-center bg-coral hover:bg-coral-dark text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm font-semibold">
              Subscribe
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Enterprise Repository -->
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Enterprise Repo</h3>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">Included</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">With paid plans</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Private repository
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                SSO/OIDC & SAML
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                RBAC permissions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Audit logging
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="block w-full text-center bg-teal-dark/20 hover:bg-teal-dark/30 text-barrel-gray py-2.5 rounded-lg transition text-sm">
              Learn More
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Barrel Console Section -->
      <div class="mb-20">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-light/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Barrel Console</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-center mb-8">Bring Your Own Cloud. We manage, you host.</p>

        <!-- Architecture Diagram -->
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
          <img src="/images/console-diagram.svg" alt="Barrel Console architecture - nodes in your cloud connecting to central control plane" class="w-full rounded-lg" />
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl border border-teal-light/30 p-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">Free</p>
                <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Up to 3 nodes</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">19<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mo</span></p>
                <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Up to 10 nodes</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">49<span class="text-lg text-barrel-gray/60">€/mo</span></p>
                <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Unlimited nodes</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-teal-dark/30 pt-6 mb-6">
              <p class="text-sm text-barrel-gray/60 text-center mb-4">Control plane for your self-hosted Barrel servers</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm max-w-md mx-auto">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Node registration & health monitoring
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Cluster topology & replication view
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Node discovery & mesh coordination
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-barrel-gray/80">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal-light mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Alerts & notifications
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="text-center">
              <a href="https://console.barrel-db.eu" class="inline-block bg-teal-light hover:bg-teal-dark text-barrel-black px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition font-semibold">
                Open Console
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What's Included Section -->
      <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto border border-teal-dark/30 mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-8">All Plans Include</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">EU-Only Data Residency</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Data never leaves European infrastructure</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">100% Open Source</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Apache 2.0. Fork it, modify it, deploy it.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">High Performance</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">&lt;5ms vector search, &lt;1ms document reads</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">GDPR Compliant</p>
              <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">Built for European data protection</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Questions?</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I self-host everything?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Yes. Both Barrel Vector and Barrel Docs are Apache 2.0 open source. You can run them on your own infrastructure with zero cost.
              Paid plans add professional support and managed hosting.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">What does "per instance" mean?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Each running database node counts as one instance. If you run 3 Barrel Vector nodes and 2 Barrel Docs nodes,
              that's 5 instances. Mix and match support levels as needed.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Do you offer annual billing?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Yes. Annual plans include 2 months free. Contact sales for annual pricing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">What is the Enterprise Repository?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              All paid support plans include access to our private Enterprise Repository with SSO/OIDC and SAML authentication,
              role-based access control (RBAC), audit logging with retention policies, and priority security patches.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-barrel-black rounded-lg border border-teal-dark/30 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">What is Barrel Console?</h4>
            <p class="text-barrel-gray/60 text-sm">
              Barrel Console is a control plane for your self-hosted Barrel servers. You run the databases on your infrastructure,
              we provide monitoring, node discovery, cluster management, and alerts. Like CockroachDB's BYOC model.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
